OL,5,G2200 The Rise & Fall of John Leslie
OL,6,     FThis hour-long documentary charts
OL,7,     Fthe rise and fall of one Britain's
OL,8,     Fmost famous TV presenters who
OL,9,     Ffound himself at the centre of a
OL,10,     Fmedia storm.
OL,11,G2300 Taggart
OL,12,     FWhen a skeleton is discovered and
OL,13,     Flinked to the disappearance of a
OL,14,     Fschoolteacher in 1939, Jardine's
OL,15,     Fteam suddenly find themselves
OL,16,     Finvestigating the pre-war case.
